        "description": "Slot Car VR (Open BETA) \n\nBringing back the nostalgia and joy of slot car racing in your home, but this time it's better!\n\nLet your imagination run wild with no limitations on track or props. The intuitive track building tool allows you to create custom circuits quickly and satisfyingly. \n\nPlay without controllers - Build track, place props and race, all without picking up a controller (well a physical one at at least!)\n\nMultiplayer - Locally and globally. Play against others in your home or race and build with friends at theirs.\n\n**** Please note, Slot Car VR is still in early development and whilst we're sure you will have a great time, we also have a whole host of thigs to come, so watch this space. We love feedback and encourage you to get in touch with us if you have any issues, find any bugs or simply have some cool ideas that maybe we haven't thought about yet.\n\nPlease join our discord to let us know how you are getting on and to help us make Slot Car VR even better *****\n\nWe hope you enjoy the game and thank you from all the team at Sandford Tech. ",
